The paper discusses a new neural network architecture that improves upon the performance of vanilla LSTM cells. This falls under the broad category of machine learning, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Given that the paper focuses on recurrent neural networks and attention mechanisms, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language), as these sub-categories are also relevant to the paper's topic.
